  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/3c3627926b82316996b1e6be2a184884.avif?t=1769255244\" width=616 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Super Night Riders</strong> is a modern arcade racing game inspired by the retro classics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are <i>Alice</i>, a beautiful and talented motorcyclist known as the <i>Red Rider</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/ccbd5511f2fe574ef951100555a3d909.poster.avif?t=1769255244\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/ccbd5511f2fe574ef951100555a3d909.webm?t=1769255244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/ccbd5511f2fe574ef951100555a3d909.mp4?t=1769255244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, your position in the race does not matter. It's all about traveling as far as possible while dodging the rival riders, and reaching each checkpoint before the timer hits zero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/dd7c7519896303e521da09288064aed1.poster.avif?t=1769255244\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/dd7c7519896303e521da09288064aed1.webm?t=1769255244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/dd7c7519896303e521da09288064aed1.mp4?t=1769255244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the races starts during the day and continue through the night right up until sunrise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/1b560e8f0475e332fbd39045c4484ca8.avif?t=1769255244\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features 2 visual styles: <i>Super</i> and <i>Classic</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/ae205c96bb90706ba3ad943af01716b2.avif?t=1769255244\" width=640 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ride through 36 beautiful stages in 6 challenging courses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/a241ef0f913da043776f3ff31375f092.avif?t=1769255244\" width=640 height=340 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>About miyu.works</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>miyu.works</i> is a one person indie game studio from France, making modern renditions of classic concepts.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/3c3627926b82316996b1e6be2a184884.avif?t=1769255244\" width=616 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Super Night Riders</strong> is a modern arcade racing game inspired by the retro classics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are <i>Alice</i>, a beautiful and talented motorcyclist known as the <i>Red Rider</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/ccbd5511f2fe574ef951100555a3d909.poster.avif?t=1769255244\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/ccbd5511f2fe574ef951100555a3d909.webm?t=1769255244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/ccbd5511f2fe574ef951100555a3d909.mp4?t=1769255244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, your position in the race does not matter. It's all about traveling as far as possible while dodging the rival riders, and reaching each checkpoint before the timer hits zero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/dd7c7519896303e521da09288064aed1.poster.avif?t=1769255244\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/dd7c7519896303e521da09288064aed1.webm?t=1769255244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/dd7c7519896303e521da09288064aed1.mp4?t=1769255244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the races starts during the day and continue through the night right up until sunrise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/1b560e8f0475e332fbd39045c4484ca8.avif?t=1769255244\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features 2 visual styles: <i>Super</i> and <i>Classic</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/ae205c96bb90706ba3ad943af01716b2.avif?t=1769255244\" width=640 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ride through 36 beautiful stages in 6 challenging courses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444000/extras/a241ef0f913da043776f3ff31375f092.avif?t=1769255244\" width=640 height=340 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>About miyu.works</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>miyu.works</i> is a one person indie game studio from France, making modern renditions of classic concepts.</p>",
